      "value": "<p><strong>Source</strong> <em>Dragonslayer's Handbook pg. 27</em></p><h3 class=\"framing\">Statistics</h3><p><strong>Cost</strong> 75 gp <strong>Weight</strong> 15 lbs.</p><p><strong>Category</strong> Ammunition; <strong>Proficiency</strong> Ammunition</p><h3 class=\"framing\">Description</h3><p>This ballista bolt is specially equipped with a net which unfurls  as the bolt flies toward its target. Unlike a standard ballista bolt,  a ballista net requires only a touch attack to hit. If a ballista  net hits, it deals no damage, but causes the target to become  entangled. An entangled creature takes a -2 penalty on attack  rolls and a -4 penalty to Dexterity, can move at only half speed,  and cannot charge or run.</p>",
